name: Vintage Shabby Boudoir Table Lamps Porcelain Angels Brass White Distressed Bases
description:
Gorgeous table lamps with porcelain cherub Angels. Lovely ornate brass footed bases on each lamp, painted a shabby chippy distressed white adds a delightful cottage look and style.   
Plug and cord is in good working order, no chips or cracks , light wear to gilt trim from vintage age.  Very lovely,  and perfect for your shabby chic, Victorian or Paris flat boudoir. 

This pair of Cherub lamps each measure 12 1/2" Up to the base where the light bulb goes. Old fashioned push in turn on and off buttons/sticks that go from one side to the other when pushed to turn on and off. The cherubs which are porcelain appear to be holding onto columns and each is very detailed. I see no chips or cracks on either lamp. The bases is the old fashioned scroll look in a square stand / base with feet on all four sides. I see only a couple of scuff marks, but not chips on the backs of the cherubs. If you would like more pictures feel free to ask. Assuming these to be very old or either someone made them to look this old by distressing as even the base for the light bulbs are painted along with the antique bases in a shabby distressed "chippy" style.  Gorgeous with just the right Antique Lace victorian shades.

name: FROZEN CHARLOTTE GERMAN DOLL NECKLACE ALTERED ART VINTAGE STEAMPUNK
description:
Steampunk  Necklace

One of a Kind Artisan Hand Crafted Steampunk Assemblage Necklace
with Antique German Bisque Porcelain Frozen Charlotte Angel Doll

Unique One of a Kind Steampunk Inspired Wearable Artwork
German Charlotte Doll Necklace

This listing is for an Artisan Hand Crafted Altered Art Steampunk Assemblage Necklace.  Designed with a Sweet Antique Frozen Charlotte Doll Angel that was made in Germany during
the 1860's. Charlotte is wearing a Pewter Crown upon her Head, Burgundy Faux Pearls, Pewter Wings, and and a Burgundy Antique  Lace Dress with Lace Wings.


The Necklace is an 18" Inch Black Silk
 Ribbon with Lobster Claw Clasp and 2 Inch Extension Chain. Each Frozen Charlotte Doll
Necklace is a One of a Kind, and not two are exactly the same
.
The Picture is the doll you will receive, please consider the photographs part of the description. Each Doll has unique characteristics and imperfections that make her a One of a Kind Original! 

More information on the Vintage Doll:
This is a One of a Kind Original Creation, and you will never see another exactly like it!
These beautiful German Bisque Porcelain dolls were dug from the grounds of a doll factory in Thuringia Germany.Many of these precious tiny dolls had been buried on the grounds of the factories because they were broken, or less than perfect. They are now being rediscovered, and are popular for using in artwork and crafts. The Necklace is an adjustable black ribbon and cord measuring approximately 16" (unfastened) with room to make shorter or loger Gith the silver adjustable chain links at the closure. The lovely German doll is a mere 2 1/2" tall with vintage lace wings and vintage lace dress wrapped around her. She also has the lovely silver toned charm wings, as stated in the above description.

name: Vintage Fifties Jestia Toy Monkey Antique Japan Faux Fur
description: Ahh The memories!  Had one of these when I was little!  The furry little Jestia Monkey on a leash.. I have researched this guy and understand that he is made in Japan and from the 1950's by "Jestia / Japan". This one has no tags. As you see he has an adorable Celluloid face. He wears Felt yellow and red pants along with his sleeves and a slightly faded (due to age) cap. His face has no flaws, His body is in great Excellent condition except maybe where his pants pull away where he sits to show the molded white form of his rear in one tiny corner..this does not show when seated. For his age I consider him in Excellent condition, displayed only in my Vintage Toy curio cabinet. His fur is very soft and his arms and legs have wires inside so that he is adjustable. He wears the cutest gold material style collar around his neck with a chain leash and a handle also of the same gold material as the collar. He does not have his sewn in tag. Measures approximately 8" tall in seated position
